The game itself is OK. However, this *paid* app is laden with all sorts of undesirable components: Chartboost, Flurry, Fortumo, SponsorPay, Arello, Heyzap. They want to track how you play the game (God knows what else), "recommend" items of interest to you, etc. not just when you play it, but also to send you messages from the cloud. If I had checked out its permissions & activities as soon as I bought it, I would not have it on my device even if they pay me! But I missed the refund window, so my only recourse will be to stay away from this developer from here onwards...
